author: Leon Blum
message: The free man is he who does not fear to go to the end of his thought.

author: Ralph Emerson
message: Great are they who see that spiritual is stronger than any material force, that thoughts rule the world.

author: Bernard Shaw
message: A life spent making mistakes is not only more honourable but more useful than a life spent in doing nothing.
title: Thought of the day

author: Lao Tzu
message: The wise man does not lay up his own treasures. The more he gives to others, the more he has for his own.
title: Thought of the day
